strings.slogan: There's a new CMS in town

strings.description: Use Firebase to host your site, store your data and manage your users. You can do all that with Firebase's free Spark plan*
strings.descriptionSecondary: It's easy to extend the CMS with your React skills. Create new templates, apps or data stores. Use JSONs to import & export anything
strings.notes: * The Blaze plan is required for Image Uploading. Thumbnail resizing is done via Cloud Functions. It can still be free for low usage.
